{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "header",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## CENTCOM reporting and disclosure lifecycle\n\nThis canvas traces an observation from the moment it occurs to the moment it becomes a public record.\n\nThe collection's modern DOW MISREPs and Range Foulers all follow this lifecycle. Understanding the pipeline explains why ==so much of every released record is redacted==, and why the unclassified tearline that reaches public consumption is often two sentences long even when the underlying record is ten pages.",
      "x": -1000,
      "y": -500,
      "width": 700,
      "height": 380,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "step1",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 1. Observation",
      "x": -700,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "step2",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 2. Standardized debrief",
      "x": -300,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "step3",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 3. Service analysis cell",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "step4",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 4. AARO aggregation",
      "x": 500,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "step5",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 5. MDR declassification",
      "x": 900,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "step6",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 6. Public release",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "platform-f15",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "05 - Platforms and Units/Platform - F-15E Strike Eagle.md",
      "x": -700,
      "y": 150,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 170,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "platform-mq9",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## MQ-9 (482 ATKS)\n21-hr ISR missions\nover Persian Gulf monitoring Iranian Navy",
      "x": -700,
      "y": 350,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "platform-f18",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "05 - Platforms and Units/Platform - MH-60R Seahawk.md",
      "x": -700,
      "y": 540,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 170,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "misrep",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## MISREP\nMission Report\n(USAF)\n\nStandard fields:\n- Operation, COCOM\n- ACEQUIP\n- AIRSIGHT events\n- GENTEXT narrative\n- EMI section\n- POC/QC/Approver",
      "x": -300,
      "y": 150,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "rfdb",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Range Fouler Debrief\n(Navy / SPEAR)\n\nStandard fields:\n- Working area, date, time\n- BUNO, side number\n- Sensor configuration\n- Shape checkboxes\n- Free narrative",
      "x": -300,
      "y": 490,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "unit-389",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "05 - Platforms and Units/Unit - 389 EFS.md",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 150,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 170,
      "color": "7"
    },
    {
      "id": "spear",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## SPEAR\nStrike Project for\nEvaluation, Analysis,\nand Reporting\n\nAnonymizes Range\nFouler reports.",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 350,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "7"
    },
    {
      "id": "paroc",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "05 - Platforms and Units/Unit - 12 AF DET 3.md",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 580,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 170,
      "color": "7"
    },
    {
      "id": "aaro",
      "type": "file",
